To install puppet on a fresh raspberry pi:

1) ssh pi@raspberrypi
2) sudo apt-get install puppet-common
3) sudo apt-get install git
4) sudo mv /etc/puppet ~
5) cd /etc
6) sudo git clone git://github.com/yorrick/puppet.git

To update raspberry pi:

1) ssh yorrick@raspberrypi
2) sudo git --git-dir=/etc/puppet/.git pull 
3) sudo puppet apply /etc/puppet/manifests/config.pp 
